CROSS-COMPILE FOR ANDROID:
 
 
 1: make make OS_ID=0.4.3 # 0.4.4 use compile options incompatible with android cross-compiler
 
 2: make TOOLS=<path-to-cross-compile-tools><cross-compile-prefix>
      e.g.
    make TOOLS=/android/android-ndk-r8b/toolchains/arm-linux-androideabi-4.8.0/prebuilt/linux-x86/bin/arm-linux-androideabi-
      (NOTE the final '-' )
   
